h5. Problem Summary:
Customer would like to return a search result where the username is the same in both reporter and assignee fields.

h5. Current Method:
You would have to search and enter the username matching them with an AND condition.
{code}
reporter = "username" AND assignee ="username"
{code}

h5. Expected Method:
Add a condition that allows user to check directly if values between fields are the same.
{code}
reporter = assignee//allows user to get all issues where reporter is the same as assignee
{code}
_Could be implemented for other user or group fields._

h5. Why:
This helps ensure that the user does not need to search for each pair that match to get the results he wants in issue navigator.

